      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Wide open. SOUTHAMPTON FLARE (3) is only just out of maiden grade but has more upside than most. Lightly raced galloper who started favourite here latest and drew clear for a strong win. Low draw and can measure up again. JULY (4) has been following a good run with a bad run, including last start when safely held here. Best figures more than measure up and gets a chance to atone. ANKLE ROLEX (5) returned to winning form here last time, racing on pace and lifting strongly to score over a shade further. Form is good and looks hard to beat again. DYNAMIC THEORY (6) returns from break. Best form stacks up and looks a key runner fresh. VALKUR (9) is coming off a better run last time when placed. Has ability and is one of the chances.",
